WEBVTT

00:00:00.670 --> 00:00:03.026
yetst bay kaset numer dray

00:00:03.201 --> 00:00:05.523
bite, dertseyln ⟨SIE⟩ vayter

00:00:05.884 --> 00:00:07.126
vos ⟨SIE⟩ gedenken.

00:00:06.508 --> 00:00:10.181
yetst heybt zikh on di mayse, farshteystu, in geto

00:00:10.407 --> 00:00:13.033
az me heybt on makhn UNK oyszidlungen.

00:00:14.727 --> 00:00:17.737
ZUHAUSE i- hob ikh ge- MEINE froy

00:00:17.737 --> 00:00:21.677
hobn gevoynt mit mir tsuzamen mit mayn kind un mayn tate.

00:00:21.898 --> 00:00:24.899
in tsveytn hoyz hot gevoynt, farshteystu

00:00:24.899 --> 00:00:26.331
⟨MEINE bruder⟩

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:29.840
der KOPELMAN vos er iz geven LANDOY's an eydem

00:00:30.201 --> 00:00:35.291
UND MEINE shvester vos zi iz geven farheyrat mit a ⟨gevise⟩ B., ikh vil dir nisht zogn dem nomen

00:00:35.803 --> 00:00:41.713
UND azoy ahin un aher farshteystu, m'hot gevoynt, un m'hot gelebt. ikh shoyn geven bin a gliklekher

00:00:41.713 --> 00:00:42.753
gevezn

00:00:42.753 --> 00:00:44.483
az ikh hob gehat a postn

00:00:44.483 --> 00:00:46.883
vos ikh bin shoyn keyn hungeriker nisht gevezn

00:00:47.413 --> 00:00:48.402
farshteyst?

00:00:48.493 --> 00:00:49.963
un m'hot ongehoybn tsu makhn

00:00:49.963 --> 00:00:54.433
oyfn UNK felder, hot men genumen di ⟨gertner⟩, m'hot gemakht, hob ikh gekrign tsugeteylt. ikh hob a

00:00:54.433 --> 00:00:55.353
a DZIALKA.

00:00:55.353 --> 00:00:56.773
a DZIALKA vos ikh hob gehat

00:00:56.773 --> 00:00:59.423
a bisl burakn, un hot gemakht vos m'hot gekent.

00:00:59.423 --> 00:01:01.463
der f- UNK

00:01:01.501 --> 00:01:03.450
ikh hob gehat burakn. ikh hob gehat

00:01:03.450 --> 00:01:04.910
kapuste, ikh hob

00:01:04.910 --> 00:01:07.680
der mayster ⟨MEIER⟩ hot mir arayngebrengt in a UNK

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:09.244
trots dem

00:01:09.317 --> 00:01:11.420
hot mir der mayster ⟨MEIER⟩ gebrengt

00:01:11.494 --> 00:01:12.652
krulikes

00:01:13.030 --> 00:01:14.840
oyf, ⟨ikh hob⟩ gehat oyf dem boydem

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:16.550
hob ikh gekhovet krulikes.

00:01:17.097 --> 00:01:20.241
mir zenen gevezn, der shver mayner, ⟨hob ikh dokh gezogt⟩ dort gevoynt

00:01:20.241 --> 00:01:22.806
⟨ZIELNA⟩ eyn un tsvontsik, hot gevoynt zayn

00:01:22.806 --> 00:01:24.485
zayns a, vi herst dos, der

00:01:24.485 --> 00:01:28.886
mayn shvoger's mit f- mitn shver, UNK zayn frier

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:35.440
UND, er hot bakumen an arbet, farshteyst, a dank ⟨tsu⟩ mayn shver, hot er bakumen an arbet, hot zikh gegrindet

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:38.270
a ⟨Poyln⟩ yugnt farvayl lager far di geto.

00:01:39.152 --> 00:01:46.014
hot mayn shver gezen, er zol krign dort an arbet, er iz gevezn, der tate hot gehat a groyse ve- verkshtel. er hot gemakht mebl

00:01:47.269 --> 00:01:54.975
UND er iz gevorn UNK iz er dort gevorn oyser di geto bay dem ⟨POLEN⟩ yugnt farvayl lager, iz er gevorn a instruktor

00:01:55.116 --> 00:01:57.476
un dort hot im shoyn nisht ge- gefelt oykh k-

00:01:57.476 --> 00:01:58.626
keyn esn.

00:01:58.626 --> 00:02:00.546
un er hot gegat dray

00:02:00.546 --> 00:02:04.053
dray shve- ts- eyn bruder un tsvey shvester in di geto

00:02:04.077 --> 00:02:06.070
un gevoynt UNK

00:02:06.070 --> 00:02:08.380
tir bay tir mit m- MEINE

00:02:08.380 --> 00:02:09.560
sh- shver

00:02:10.370 --> 00:02:12.950
azoy az mayn shver hot oykh gegat. mayn shver

00:02:12.950 --> 00:02:16.455
hot vayter gekrign, hot men geendert di yidishe gimnazye bay dem

00:02:16.468 --> 00:02:20.163
iz dos hot ge- heyst oyf di UNK. UNK hot der gast geheysn

00:02:20.163 --> 00:02:22.599
dos iz geven barn LU- barn park der oybn.

00:02:22.943 --> 00:02:24.855
iz gevezn. UNK hot geboyt di

00:02:24.855 --> 00:02:26.635
hobn zey geboyt di yidishe gimnazye

00:02:26.635 --> 00:02:28.125
un er hot gekrign dort

00:02:28.125 --> 00:02:30.135
tsu endikn dos do, un dort hot zikh gegri-

00:02:30.135 --> 00:02:31.765
gevorn GESTAPO

00:02:31.765 --> 00:02:34.835
di ershte tra- apteylung fun GESTAPO

00:02:34.835 --> 00:02:37.849
in dort yidish geme- hobn UNK ongehoybn dort

00:02:37.849 --> 00:02:39.939
farshteystu tsu

00:02:39.939 --> 00:02:43.590
renovirn, tsu makhn in ordenung, vayl INZYNIER Gutman, z- mayn shver

00:02:43.590 --> 00:02:47.450
hot er getseylt, hot men dort gemakht, un m'hot gemolt. m'hot gemakht in ordenung.

00:02:47.968 --> 00:02:49.936
mit eyn mol, farshteystu

00:02:51.327 --> 00:02:53.008
iz gekumen tsu geyn a mentsh

00:02:53.149 --> 00:02:54.206
tsu mir

00:02:54.583 --> 00:02:59.892
un hot gezogt tsu mir "her oys. ikh vil fun dir finef hundert dolar.

00:03:00.456 --> 00:03:03.622
oyb vest mir nisht gebn, vestu shoyn zen vos vet zayn mit dir."

00:03:04.084 --> 00:03:07.672
ongekhapt un aroysgevorfn, UNK "gey UNK mit di fis."

00:03:08.337 --> 00:03:09.630
ahin aher

00:03:10.378 --> 00:03:13.105
ikh veys nisht vi s'iz gevezn. mit eyn molt

00:03:13.163 --> 00:03:15.654
hot men genumen mayn bruder aroyf

00:03:15.660 --> 00:03:17.814
fun vanet er hot gevust veys ikh nisht

00:03:18.040 --> 00:03:20.350
farshteystu. ikh bin nisht gevezn in di heym.

00:03:20.350 --> 00:03:23.230
m'hot bahaltn, zey hobn bahaltn alts oyfn boydem

00:03:23.230 --> 00:03:25.458
tsvishn ts- di podloge

00:03:25.482 --> 00:03:31.692
un di s- ts- dem tsvishn iz UNK gevezn, un lere, hot men dort bahaltn

00:03:31.692 --> 00:03:34.882
UNK gelt mit alts, un ayngemoyert in keler

00:03:34.882 --> 00:03:37.715
hobn zey ayngemoyert, farshteystu, untn ales.

00:03:37.716 --> 00:03:40.528
iz gekumen tsu geyn UNK ⟨eyn molt⟩

00:03:40.753 --> 00:03:44.290
her ikh, farshteystu, mayn bruder hot men genumen aroyf in di KRIPO.

00:03:44.922 --> 00:03:48.240
m'hot im gut tsehakt, farshteystu, mit gornisht

00:03:48.837 --> 00:03:51.801
un er iz gezitsn in di KRI- ikh hob nisht gehat keyn anung derfun.

00:03:52.414 --> 00:03:54.855
ikh bin dokh avekgan in di fri aroys oyf di arbet

00:03:55.232 --> 00:03:57.301
ALSO mit eyn molt ruft men mikh

00:03:58.354 --> 00:03:59.495
in di

00:03:59.721 --> 00:04:00.575
KRIPO.

00:04:02.235 --> 00:04:06.923
fregt mikh, ahin, aher, zog ikh "ikh veys" neyn, antshuldik, ikh h- hob fargesn dos vikhtikste.

00:04:06.923 --> 00:04:09.290
hob ikh dos gehert az mayn bruder iz in di KRIPO

00:04:09.290 --> 00:04:12.193
un m'hot gegebn, un ver s'iz gevezn bar im

00:04:12.193 --> 00:04:14.003
un ⟨zi hot⟩ gezogt, mir veln gebn

00:04:14.003 --> 00:04:15.393
iz mir nisht gut gevorn

00:04:15.393 --> 00:04:18.620
hob ikh moyre gekrign, ⟨hob ikh⟩ gezen a- a- der mentsh veyst vos tut zikh

00:04:18.620 --> 00:04:21.743
az me zol m- nisht tun gornisht, bin ikh gelofn tsum prezes

00:04:21.743 --> 00:04:23.343
un dertseylt di mayse

00:04:23.343 --> 00:04:26.118
zogt der prezes "ikh hob dem mentsh oyf di oygn

00:04:26.118 --> 00:04:28.938
un geb on vos du host." m'hot mikh aroyfgefirt

00:04:28.938 --> 00:04:30.198
bald aroysgelozt oyfn

00:04:30.198 --> 00:04:33.072
⟨tsum⟩ BALUTER plats tsu dem prezes, tsum prezident

00:04:33.072 --> 00:04:34.842
komi- oyberkomisar FUCHS

00:04:34.842 --> 00:04:36.462
un ikh bin aroyfgekumen oyvn

00:04:36.462 --> 00:04:37.796
un ikh hob gegebn

00:04:37.796 --> 00:04:40.846
vos m'hot bahaltn, un vu un ven un vos.

00:04:40.846 --> 00:04:43.646
m'hot mir gezogt. ikh hob dokh nisht gevust, der shver hot mir dos gezogt.

00:04:43.967 --> 00:04:47.877
ahin aher, zogt der pre- komisar FUCHS, OBERKOMMISAR FUCHS

00:04:47.877 --> 00:04:49.457
"ikh kum morgn tsu geyn

00:04:49.457 --> 00:04:50.957
vestu geyn in shtot arayn.

00:04:50.975 --> 00:04:52.545
⟨tsu⟩ forn in shtot arayn."

00:04:52.545 --> 00:04:55.217
hot er gegebn a geshrey, "her ⟨KRUZONT⟩

00:04:55.324 --> 00:04:56.668
KOMMEN SIE HEREIN.

00:04:57.400 --> 00:05:01.123
SIE FAHREN MORGEN IN DIE STADT MIT DIESEN, ACHT UHR"

00:05:01.180 --> 00:05:04.009
in di fri akhte zol ikh kumen dortn UNK in shtot.

00:05:04.352 --> 00:05:08.330
akht in di fri morgn bin ikh gekumen tsu forn UNK in di KRIPO

00:05:08.330 --> 00:05:09.952
hot er gehat UNK

00:05:09.952 --> 00:05:12.942
iz gevezn eyner, se heyst Gutman

00:05:12.942 --> 00:05:15.642
iz er geven der f- der kutsher mit ferd

00:05:15.642 --> 00:05:19.352
hot er gehat a britshke, a yidi- a yid. er iz geforn far di, mit di ferd

00:05:19.352 --> 00:05:20.601
dort ahin

00:05:20.601 --> 00:05:24.371
iz gekumen tsu forn UNK dort gevezn, ALSO m'iz geforn in shtot arayn.

00:05:24.371 --> 00:05:27.106
geforn in shtot arayn dort vu ikh hob gevoynt

00:05:27.106 --> 00:05:28.686
un mayn shvoger hot gevoynt

00:05:28.686 --> 00:05:30.716
gekumen in shtot arayn d- der, der,

00:05:30.716 --> 00:05:32.594
der UNK heyst ⟨zi⟩

00:05:32.820 --> 00:05:39.243
der UNK iz geven der zelber alt- an alter UNK, hot mikh gezen, hot er mir arumgekhapt "KOPELMAN, du lebst UNK"

00:05:39.322 --> 00:05:41.572
"yo." iz tsugeganen der

00:05:41.572 --> 00:05:43.112
hot men im gegebn aza

00:05:43.112 --> 00:05:44.502
knal in, in ponem arayn

00:05:44.502 --> 00:05:45.402
der bokser

00:05:45.402 --> 00:05:46.952
iz fun vanet hob ikh gevust er iz a bokser?

00:05:46.952 --> 00:05:49.627
zogt er "ikh bin a bokser" zogt er. UNK a VOLKSDEUTSCH.

00:05:49.627 --> 00:05:52.187
"ikh vel dir" zogt er "oyshakn di tseyn mit a yid

00:05:52.187 --> 00:05:55.436
vestu di- gedenkst UNK nokh a molt az zolst nisht tun.

00:05:55.436 --> 00:05:57.846
ikh bin a bokser" zogt er. "ikh d- knal dikh avek."

00:05:57.846 --> 00:06:01.416
shoyn, dos iz geven dos gants. yetst geyt men aroyf tsu mir in di voynung.

00:06:01.416 --> 00:06:03.666
me kumt aroyf tsu mir tsu di voynung

00:06:04.696 --> 00:06:06.100
klingt mikh

00:06:06.100 --> 00:06:08.150
UNK ferdn shtok hob ikh gevoynt.

00:06:08.150 --> 00:06:09.020
me klingt

00:06:09.020 --> 00:06:09.880
efnt

00:06:09.880 --> 00:06:11.590
a man der tir

00:06:12.330 --> 00:06:14.730
un der iz gevezn, der iz a OBEN-

00:06:14.730 --> 00:06:18.790
UNTERSTURMFUHRER ⟨ober⟩ OBERSTURMFUHRER, der bokser vos hot geheysn ⟨KRUZON⟩

00:06:18.790 --> 00:06:22.314
zogt er UNK fregt er "vos vilstu?" ⟨freg⟩ zikh dermanen

00:06:22.314 --> 00:06:24.314
zogt er "ikh vil arayngeyn do" zogt er

00:06:24.314 --> 00:06:26.905
der yid hot do bahaltn zakhn.

00:06:26.905 --> 00:06:28.415
UNK

00:06:28.415 --> 00:06:30.218
zogt er ⟨tsu mir⟩ "tsum tayvl

00:06:30.218 --> 00:06:32.098
RAUS fun HIER."

00:06:32.098 --> 00:06:33.148
gey avek fun HIER

00:06:33.148 --> 00:06:35.057
zogt er "zestu do vos ikh bin?

00:06:35.057 --> 00:06:37.377
UNK muz KOMMEN aza range tsu mir

00:06:37.377 --> 00:06:38.677
⟨gib⟩"

00:06:38.677 --> 00:06:40.512
un ot lozt im nisht arayn.

00:06:40.512 --> 00:06:42.732
vos hot pasirt? zogt er

00:06:43.003 --> 00:06:44.937
der bokser, der ⟨KRUZON⟩

00:06:46.108 --> 00:06:47.968
tsu dem Gutman

00:06:47.968 --> 00:06:49.198
dem kutsher

00:06:49.198 --> 00:06:50.438
un tsu ⟨WOJCIECHOSKIN⟩

00:06:50.438 --> 00:06:51.578
zol mikh hitn

00:06:51.578 --> 00:06:52.998
un er geyt arunter

00:06:52.998 --> 00:06:54.698
tsum UNK GESTAPO

00:06:54.698 --> 00:06:57.425
oyf di KILINSKIEGO hundert akht un tsvontsik

00:06:57.600 --> 00:06:59.073
dort iz di GESTAPO

00:06:59.073 --> 00:07:01.883
geyt er arunter. iz ho- UNK hot er mikh gehitn

00:07:01.883 --> 00:07:03.619
un der iz avekgegangen.

00:07:03.996 --> 00:07:07.186
s'hot gedoyert efsher a halbe sho, iz gekumen tsu forn

00:07:07.186 --> 00:07:09.676
a, a militer, s'iz gekumen tsu forn

00:07:09.676 --> 00:07:10.596
der shef

00:07:10.596 --> 00:07:13.796
fun UNK GESTAPO, a pulkovnik oder a general

00:07:13.796 --> 00:07:15.405
er heyst SCHMIDT

00:07:15.405 --> 00:07:18.235
un mitge- aroyfgeganen tsunezamen. m'iz aroyfgekumen oyvn

00:07:18.235 --> 00:07:19.840
hot er ongeklapt, zogt er

00:07:19.840 --> 00:07:21.236
"GENERAL SCHMIDT"

00:07:21.715 --> 00:07:25.911
un der hot gezogt, pulkovnik dort, ikh veys UNK ⟨ongerufn⟩ mit zayn range ⟨ort⟩

00:07:26.305 --> 00:07:28.082
"JA," hot er arayngelozt.

00:07:28.082 --> 00:07:32.815
demolt hot er shoyn arayngelozt. az er hot m- genumen vos m'hot dort gefunen, m'hot aroysgenumen

00:07:32.815 --> 00:07:34.348
hot men gehat bay dem

00:07:34.455 --> 00:07:37.695
in di g- in di ECKE iz gevezn a UNK

00:07:37.695 --> 00:07:40.285
UNK

00:07:40.285 --> 00:07:41.655
UNK

00:07:41.655 --> 00:07:42.775
UNK

00:07:42.775 --> 00:07:46.164
UNK

00:07:46.164 --> 00:07:49.314
UNK

00:07:49.314 --> 00:07:52.543
un m'hot bahaltn untn arayngepakt ales ⟨dos vos m'hot⟩ gehat

00:07:53.633 --> 00:07:56.392
un hot men dort geefnt, un m'hot ales aroysgenumen.

00:07:56.392 --> 00:07:58.362
un m'iz avekgeforn.

00:07:58.452 --> 00:07:59.019
shoyn.

00:08:00.763 --> 00:08:02.360
dray tog shpeter

00:08:02.670 --> 00:08:06.169
ruft men mikh tsu GESTA- tsum KRIPO

00:08:06.169 --> 00:08:09.094
der ⟨SUTTER⟩. ikh kum aroyf, oyvn aroyf

00:08:09.673 --> 00:08:13.548
zogt er, zogt tsu mir, gey ikh UNK a hitl ongetun fun tramvay

00:08:13.605 --> 00:08:15.320
zogt er "tu dos oys."

00:08:15.529 --> 00:08:17.517
UNK ikh bin a SLUZBOWY man

00:08:17.517 --> 00:08:18.783
vil er mikh nisht shlogn.

00:08:18.783 --> 00:08:19.913
"tu dos oys."

00:08:19.913 --> 00:08:21.682
hob ikh es oysgetun. zogt er

00:08:22.144 --> 00:08:23.504
git er, er ruft

00:08:23.504 --> 00:08:27.674
"breng arayn der pol- UNK" mayn bruder. hot men arayngebrengt mayn bruder, tsehakt, tseshlogn

00:08:27.674 --> 00:08:28.724
zogt er "zest

00:08:28.724 --> 00:08:32.134
az ikh bin UNK ot di UNK az d'host oysbahaltn alts vos ikh hob gegebn

00:08:32.792 --> 00:08:35.148
zest vi er zet oys, vestu oyszen."

00:08:37.078 --> 00:08:38.287
kh'hob dos gezen

00:08:38.715 --> 00:08:39.907
zog ikh tsun im

00:08:40.403 --> 00:08:41.882
"vos vilstu fun mir?

00:08:42.124 --> 00:08:45.290
yo, s'iz, alts shtimt. kh'hob es opgegebn."

00:08:47.300 --> 00:08:52.412
"vu hostu es opgegebn?" "tsum zekstn politsey revir. m'iz gevezn in shtot, hob ikh ales aroysgegebn."

00:08:52.840 --> 00:08:54.622
"fun vanet hostu dos gevust?"

00:08:55.810 --> 00:08:59.266
zog ikh, ikh zog ikh UNK gezogt aykh di UNK

00:08:59.266 --> 00:09:01.828
s'iz gekumen tsu mir tsu geyn der un der man

00:09:02.172 --> 00:09:04.572
a B., er heyst mit dem nomen B.

00:09:04.572 --> 00:09:07.782
un er hot farshteystu gevolt fun mir finef hundert dolar

00:09:07.782 --> 00:09:09.182
un ikh hob nisht gegebn

00:09:09.182 --> 00:09:10.702
hot er gezogt ⟨nebekh⟩

00:09:10.702 --> 00:09:13.142
'vestu shoyn zen vos vest kumen, vos vest kumen mit dir.'

00:09:13.142 --> 00:09:15.902
⟨hot er⟩ mir dos gezogt, bin ikh geganen tsum prezes

00:09:15.902 --> 00:09:18.112
un ikh hob es gezogt. hot der prezes gezogt 'gey aroyf.'"

00:09:18.112 --> 00:09:20.412
⟨nor iz⟩ opgegebn. "azoy" zogt er "vart do."

00:09:21.088 --> 00:09:24.028
un mayn bruder iz, hot men im arayngefirt, un ikh bin gezitsn.

00:09:24.028 --> 00:09:25.698
m'hot geshikt nokh dem soykher.

00:09:26.978 --> 00:09:28.518
nokh dem men- nokh dem yid.

00:09:28.518 --> 00:09:30.188
m'hot gebrengt dem yid

00:09:30.522 --> 00:09:31.444
aroyf

00:09:31.483 --> 00:09:33.502
hot er arayngerufn mayn bruder

00:09:33.745 --> 00:09:35.798
un hot gezogt tsu mayn bruder azoy.

00:09:36.040 --> 00:09:39.324
"du host gekrign tsehakt. shlog im vifl du kenst."

00:09:39.990 --> 00:09:43.998
mayn bruder iz geven tsehakt, hot nisht gekent oyfheybn di hant. zogt er "UNK ikh ⟨dervayzn⟩ vos me tut"

00:09:43.998 --> 00:09:45.398
un er hot im ongehoybn

00:09:45.398 --> 00:09:46.598
tsu gebn azoy

00:09:46.598 --> 00:09:49.598
un azoy un ahin un aher. m'hot im gut tseklapt

00:09:49.598 --> 00:09:51.198
un m'hot mikh bafrayt

00:09:51.198 --> 00:09:53.011
un m'hot mayn bruder bafrayt.

00:09:53.011 --> 00:09:55.201
mayn bruder hot nisht gelebt lang.

00:09:55.201 --> 00:09:57.887
hot gelebt efsher tsvey vokhn. m'hot untergehakt di lungen im

00:09:58.315 --> 00:10:00.547
un ikh bin geblibn bafrayt dem mentshn.

00:10:00.547 --> 00:10:01.880
vos hot pasirt?

00:10:01.880 --> 00:10:03.270
pasirt ot

00:10:03.360 --> 00:10:05.531
hot mikh gerufn arop der prezes

00:10:05.638 --> 00:10:08.534
un der prezes iz geganen, ot der mentsh avekgeshikt.

00:10:08.541 --> 00:10:11.151
UNK ⟨demolt⟩ nisht gevust tsu UNK AUSCHWITZ oder

00:10:11.151 --> 00:10:13.431
tsu, tsu keyn, ergets andersh. ikh veys nisht.

00:10:13.431 --> 00:10:14.651
farshteyst?

00:10:14.651 --> 00:10:15.871
dos iz a yid gevezn.

00:10:15.871 --> 00:10:18.411
iz dos gevo- dos iz geven di mayse. nu

00:10:18.767 --> 00:10:26.017
vayter hot zikh ongehoybn UNK mayn shver hot dort gearbet. zenen gekumen, hot er di mentshn fir a zeyger, me darf aruntertsulozn di mentshn fun di arbet

00:10:26.277 --> 00:10:28.147
di oyf di NOWOBUDOWA

00:10:28.147 --> 00:10:30.347
zey hobn gearbet in droysn, shoyn geputst

00:10:30.347 --> 00:10:31.807
dos hoyz

00:10:31.807 --> 00:10:34.527
un mit eyn mol iz dos, s'iz shoyn gan arop, fertik gevezn.

00:10:34.527 --> 00:10:36.702
shoyn oystsu- tsu tun di arbet. gekumen

00:10:36.702 --> 00:10:38.499
di GESTAPO k- a kontrol

00:10:38.499 --> 00:10:44.279
hot der shver ongehoybn tsu shrayen "geyts aroyf tsurik" UNK aroyfgelofn ⟨vos⟩ mayn shver ⟨volt⟩ nisht badarft, iz aroyfgelofn a UNK

00:10:44.279 --> 00:10:46.211
⟨derlign⟩ di breter oyf di leyter

00:10:46.211 --> 00:10:47.520
oyf dem ⟨zenen zey shoyn⟩ do

00:10:47.520 --> 00:10:52.035
hot zey gegebn a ⟨shup⟩, un er iz gefloygn aroyf, un er iz geharget gevorn. m'hot im gebrengt arayn in di geto

00:10:52.035 --> 00:10:54.454
hot zikh geendikt UNK undzere zorg gevorn

00:10:54.454 --> 00:10:56.698
un der vos iz gevezn, vos hot undz

00:10:56.698 --> 00:11:01.148
gemasert iz gevezn oykh an eygener a la- a bisl an eygener.

00:11:00.195 --> 00:11:01.280
a korev.

00:11:01.148 --> 00:11:02.894
nu, ayo, yo

00:11:02.894 --> 00:11:05.016
ahin aher, hot men shoyn gehat tsores.

00:11:05.376 --> 00:11:07.564
yetst hot zikh ongehoybn vayter di

00:11:07.570 --> 00:11:10.022
oyszidlung vos mer un mer.

00:11:10.022 --> 00:11:12.306
ikh hob gemuzt loyfn mit

00:11:12.430 --> 00:11:15.010
bay yeder oyszidlung bin ikh mitgevezn.

00:11:15.010 --> 00:11:15.980
far vos?

00:11:15.980 --> 00:11:17.580
kh'hob gehat a liste fun hundert un f-

00:11:17.580 --> 00:11:19.480
un zeks un fuftsik mentshn

00:11:19.480 --> 00:11:20.260
⟨vos den⟩

00:11:20.260 --> 00:11:22.010
zayn, di froyen mit di kinder

00:11:22.010 --> 00:11:23.628
hot men nisht getort rirn.

00:11:23.628 --> 00:11:28.202
un m'hot sh- ale hot men UNK oyszidlung, hot men aruntergerufn ale oyfn hoyf

00:11:28.326 --> 00:11:36.099
un m'hot oysgeshtelt tsu di reye, un m'hot gezogt, hob ikh gezogt dos iz mayn mentsh, un dos iz zayne kinder

00:11:36.753 --> 00:11:37.593
avek

00:11:37.593 --> 00:11:39.403
UNK avekgenumen. dos iz dayn mentsh m-

00:11:39.403 --> 00:11:41.193
azoy bin ikh mitgelofn iberal.

00:11:41.193 --> 00:11:43.393
⟨az⟩ ikh hob nisht gehat a molt a vemen, hob UNK

00:11:43.393 --> 00:11:47.177
⟨tsveye⟩ fun dray man hob ikh UNK zey getrofn in WASHINGTON oyfn

00:11:47.177 --> 00:11:48.927
vi heyst dos, oyfn kongres

00:11:49.335 --> 00:11:50.577
⟨fun⟩ HOLOCAUST.

00:11:50.685 --> 00:11:53.176
hob ikh gezen, hob ikh gezogt UNK a sakh molt.

00:11:53.453 --> 00:11:57.598
eyn molt iz gevezn, es iz gekumen tsu geyn oyf di gas vos ikh voyn.

00:11:57.756 --> 00:11:58.926
ikh hob gevoynt

00:11:58.926 --> 00:11:59.986
⟨LWOWSKA⟩ finef.

00:11:59.986 --> 00:12:01.386
s'iz durkhgeganen

00:12:01.386 --> 00:12:03.536
oyf di BRZEZINER tsvey un fertsik

00:12:03.536 --> 00:12:07.503
BRZEZINER tsvey un fertsik iz geven di tsentrale fun ⟨fleyshn⟩ kelers.

00:12:07.503 --> 00:12:09.043
dort hot men gemakht a UNK

00:12:09.043 --> 00:12:11.143
dort iz gevez- dos hob ikh dort gevoynt.

00:12:11.143 --> 00:12:12.933
ikh hob gevoynt oyfn parter

00:12:13.737 --> 00:12:18.222
un oyfn tsv-, in tsveytn shtok hot gevoynt eyner vos hot geheysn KOPLOWICZ.

00:12:18.222 --> 00:12:20.987
ikh heys KOPELMAN. er hot geheysn KOPLOWICZ.

00:12:21.921 --> 00:12:24.986
vos hot pasirt? ALSO m'iz gekumen oyf di LWOWSKA gas

00:12:25.684 --> 00:12:27.014
tsu makhn di

00:12:27.014 --> 00:12:29.655
di sele- aroys- aroystsurufn di mentshn avekshikn

00:12:29.655 --> 00:12:32.205
oyf di andere zayt, az ikh hob ⟨gevoynt⟩ LWOWSKA finef

00:12:32.205 --> 00:12:33.930
iz geven LWOWSKA akht.

00:12:33.930 --> 00:12:35.831
dort hot gevoynt a MELAMUD.

00:12:35.831 --> 00:12:37.153
geheysn MELAMUD

00:12:37.328 --> 00:12:39.802
mit a por shvester mit tsvey brider

00:12:40.365 --> 00:12:42.654
ikh, s'iz nisht der melamed vi ikh hob gemeynt oykhet

00:12:43.015 --> 00:12:44.021
ahin aher

00:12:44.247 --> 00:12:46.783
er hot gearbet bay mir. er iz geven oykh a yung yingl

00:12:46.783 --> 00:12:48.913
MELAMUD. er iz geven der tsveyter GONEC.

00:12:48.913 --> 00:12:50.713
arayngekumen oyf dem hoyf

00:12:50.713 --> 00:12:52.003
iz dort gevezn

00:12:52.003 --> 00:12:54.113
a selektsye, hob ikh gezen

00:12:54.113 --> 00:12:56.673
dem MELAMUDn, hot er gezogt "dos iz mayne shvester"

00:12:56.673 --> 00:12:59.499
vayl di tate mame iz nisht gevezn, shoyn ⟨genumen⟩ avekgeshikt

00:12:59.499 --> 00:13:00.947
m'hot zey bafrayt.

00:13:01.982 --> 00:13:05.322
shoyn, zenen mir geganen ariber, zenen zey geganen ariber oyf di tsveyte zayt.

00:13:05.322 --> 00:13:08.092
oyf di tsveyte zayt aribertsugeyn, hot der, der

00:13:08.092 --> 00:13:09.325
KOPLOWICZ

00:13:09.325 --> 00:13:11.910
iz gevezn oyf, in boydem iz geven a ⟨KOMIN⟩

00:13:11.910 --> 00:13:14.270
UNK der boydem iz, gehat azoy UNK

00:13:14.270 --> 00:13:17.620
un der ⟨KOMIN⟩ geyt glaykh, iz er hot zikh bahaltn untern ⟨KOMIN⟩.

00:13:17.620 --> 00:13:19.145
oyf a tsveytn ⟨KOMIN⟩ iz gelign

00:13:19.145 --> 00:13:22.545
di, di tsvey m- yingelekh mit der froy hobn zikh bahaltn oyfn boydem

00:13:22.545 --> 00:13:23.165
un der

00:13:23.165 --> 00:13:26.111
fun dakh iz geven UNK, der boydem UNK iz geven iz geven a fentster ontsukukn

00:13:26.111 --> 00:13:27.941
oyf dem BRZEZINER gas.

00:13:28.091 --> 00:13:30.211
un er hot gekumen dort ahin

00:13:30.211 --> 00:13:31.996
⟨zenen mir⟩ arayngekumen un hoyf arayn

00:13:31.996 --> 00:13:38.294
UNK iz er aroyf d- gelofn in di shtub zen tsi ale zenen aruntergelofn, iz er gelofn oyfn boydem aroyf, hot er gekukt

00:13:38.294 --> 00:13:41.544
hot er gezen s'loyft UNK loyft UNK loyft a yungenmantshik.

00:13:41.544 --> 00:13:43.474
vi hot er geheysn? ⟨SZMULEWICZ⟩

00:13:43.474 --> 00:13:45.267
geheysn SZMU- gevoynt lebn mir

00:13:45.267 --> 00:13:46.707
iz gelofn

00:13:46.707 --> 00:13:49.097
hot er genumen fun oyvn, un hot geshosn

00:13:49.097 --> 00:13:50.327
hot im nisht getrofn

00:13:50.327 --> 00:13:52.382
hot er tsuri- er hot zikh gegebn a varf anider.

00:13:52.382 --> 00:13:53.852
a kluger yung gevezn.

00:13:55.324 --> 00:13:59.013
nor vos ⟨iz⟩? m'iz aruntergan tsu geyn, hot ⟨men im⟩ gefregt "far vos bistu antlofn?"

00:13:59.020 --> 00:14:03.960
zogt er "ikh bin antlofn? ikh bin nisht antlofn. ikh bin gelofn ⟨vayl ikh hob do di⟩ sluzhbe. kh'hob do di dinst bay di

00:14:03.960 --> 00:14:05.320
bay dem

00:14:05.449 --> 00:14:08.176
der fleysh tsentrale." aha?

00:14:09.212 --> 00:14:10.512
lebn im

00:14:10.512 --> 00:14:12.512
iz gelofn a tsveyter fun tsveyte zayt.

00:14:12.512 --> 00:14:14.972
er iz oykhet, ikh hob nisht gevust ver dos iz

00:14:14.972 --> 00:14:16.132
hot er im dershosn.

00:14:16.132 --> 00:14:17.202
der zelber

00:14:17.202 --> 00:14:18.292
der zelber bokser.

00:14:18.292 --> 00:14:19.723
hot er geheysn ⟨KRUZON⟩.

00:14:19.723 --> 00:14:21.795
azoy hot men gemakht a selektsye

00:14:21.885 --> 00:14:23.637
un m'hot geganen vayter.

00:14:23.637 --> 00:14:25.879
yetst, farshteystu, iz ongehoybn tsu kumen

00:14:26.728 --> 00:14:28.173
⟨vos zoln mir vayter tun?⟩

00:14:29.462 --> 00:14:31.211
m'vet aheymkumen tsu geyn

00:14:31.318 --> 00:14:38.484
d- fun eyn selektsye biz a tsveyte hot gedoyert a akht tog, tsvey vokhn. s'iz nisht gevezn yede tog keyn selektsye.

00:14:38.912 --> 00:14:41.795
mit eyn mol farshteystu, ikh hob shoyn gevust

00:14:41.795 --> 00:14:43.745
UNK s'vet zayn a s- a

00:14:43.745 --> 00:14:45.265
oyszidlung, hob ikh yo gevust.

00:14:45.265 --> 00:14:46.915
fun vanet hob ikh dos gevust?

00:14:46.915 --> 00:14:48.285
vayl di daytshn

00:14:48.345 --> 00:14:51.072
torn nisht araynkumen in di geto arayn ven es iz a selektsye.

00:14:51.585 --> 00:14:53.425
der ⟨MEIER⟩ hot nisht getort araynkumen.

00:14:53.425 --> 00:14:55.075
hot ⟨MEIER⟩ mir gezogt "KOPELMAN

00:14:55.075 --> 00:14:56.055
zolstu visn

00:14:56.462 --> 00:14:59.865
me kumt sh- i- mir kumen nisht, iz arayn donershtik, kumen mir n- nisht."

00:15:00.276 --> 00:15:02.683
hob ikh shoyn gevust vos iz. bin ikh aheymgekumen

00:15:02.841 --> 00:15:06.733
⟨nebekh⟩ der tate mayner, di froy mit di kinder

00:15:08.055 --> 00:15:11.120
s- kh'hob shoyn UNK tsores, kh'hob shoyn gevust vos zay- az s'vet zayn a tsore.

00:15:11.312 --> 00:15:13.199
kurts tsu der zakh, farshteystu

00:15:13.199 --> 00:15:14.310
mit eyn molt

00:15:15.210 --> 00:15:18.072
iz a selektsye nisht di zayt geto

00:15:18.096 --> 00:15:22.566
mayn froy hot er ⟨getsaygt⟩ do gezogt UNK andere zayt geto di brik aribertsugeyn

00:15:22.566 --> 00:15:23.466
dort iz a

00:15:23.466 --> 00:15:25.016
groyse oyszidlung.

00:15:25.016 --> 00:15:28.820
di geto, di oyszidlungen zenen gevezn, di SPERRE heyst dos do

00:15:28.820 --> 00:15:30.850
iz gevezn fun di fri

00:15:31.495 --> 00:15:33.895
di hekhstn biz halb tsvey.

00:15:33.895 --> 00:15:35.525
eynse, tsveye

00:15:35.525 --> 00:15:37.255
iz shoyn nisht gevezn, hobn zey geendikt.

00:15:37.255 --> 00:15:39.095
zenen nisht avek, shoyn shtendik.

00:15:39.820 --> 00:15:42.200
nu, muz men dokh loyfn ariber. s'iz

00:15:42.200 --> 00:15:45.717
a do az ikh hob dort di mentshn voynen, voynen mentshn vos arbetn bay mir oyser

00:15:45.717 --> 00:15:47.037
fun di andere zayt geto.

00:15:47.040 --> 00:15:49.397
bin ikh ⟨ALSO⟩ avekgelofn in di geto.

00:15:49.397 --> 00:15:52.717
nu, hot zikh ongehoybn in di geto UNK SPERRE, me ruft ⟨arop⟩, se loyfn di

00:15:52.717 --> 00:15:53.633
di mentshn

00:15:53.633 --> 00:15:55.363
vos zey arbetn in BALUTER plats

00:15:55.363 --> 00:15:58.438
di andere hobn nisht gevust az dos iz di mentshn. m'hot gemeynt dos iz militer

00:15:59.322 --> 00:16:01.948
vos hot pasirt? pasirt, farshteystu

00:16:02.106 --> 00:16:03.470
oyfn khazer mark.

00:16:03.470 --> 00:16:05.057
veys a khazer mark iz gevezn?

00:16:05.057 --> 00:16:06.517
shteyen nor, zenen slupn

00:16:06.517 --> 00:16:09.707
fun kuen UNK me ⟨bindt zey TIERn⟩ fun beton

00:16:09.707 --> 00:16:11.917
TIERn, khazeyrim, ferd

00:16:11.917 --> 00:16:14.554
iz do azoy dos. mit eyn mol kumt on tsu forn

00:16:15.201 --> 00:16:16.308
FUCHS

00:16:16.450 --> 00:16:19.127
mit SCHMIDT, a tsveyter fartreter, SCHMIDT

00:16:19.825 --> 00:16:21.255
der bokser iz nishto.

00:16:21.255 --> 00:16:22.605
der, mit di khevre

00:16:22.605 --> 00:16:23.905
ikh shtey dernebn

00:16:23.905 --> 00:16:25.815
ikh shtey v- ongerukt, lomir zogn

00:16:25.815 --> 00:16:27.575
azoy vi do, un ikh shtey do

00:16:27.575 --> 00:16:30.832
un loyf umedum mit mit, mit di, ikh muz loyfn mit tsu d-

00:16:30.832 --> 00:16:32.602
zogn vu di mentshn arbetn.

00:16:33.809 --> 00:16:36.699
un mit eyn molt hot ge- hot ge- heybn on mentshn tsu antloyfn.

00:16:36.699 --> 00:16:38.969
UNK tsu bahaltn zikh arayn in di hayzer arayn

00:16:38.969 --> 00:16:40.489
iz er tsugeforn mit dem JEEP

00:16:42.607 --> 00:16:43.747
tsu dem slup

00:16:43.747 --> 00:16:45.557
un s'hot zikh arayngedrukt

00:16:46.909 --> 00:16:49.231
un er ken nisht, er ken nisht vayter geyn.

00:16:49.558 --> 00:16:51.647
kurts tsu di zakh, vos pasirt?

00:16:51.647 --> 00:16:53.124
sh- ikh shtey dokh dort.

00:16:53.124 --> 00:16:55.654
ikh bin ⟨dokh⟩ der OBERMEISTER fun ⟨ELEKTRESTRASSE⟩ UNK ikh loyf

00:16:55.654 --> 00:16:56.484
zey kenen mikh

00:16:56.484 --> 00:16:58.516
vayl ikh loyf ⟨tsurik mit zey⟩ mit zey dermit.

00:16:58.516 --> 00:17:00.031
zogt er tsu mir "kum aher."

00:17:01.388 --> 00:17:02.693
p- er b-

00:17:02.693 --> 00:17:04.268
UNK

00:17:04.746 --> 00:17:07.106
zog ikh "ikh ken nisht. dos iz nisht mayn baruf."

00:17:07.106 --> 00:17:08.656
ikh vil aroysbeygn di UNK

00:17:08.656 --> 00:17:10.376
zikh arayngeboygn dos gantse

00:17:10.376 --> 00:17:11.096
der

00:17:11.490 --> 00:17:12.960
UNK

00:17:12.550 --> 00:17:13.410
⟨TAMBON⟩

00:17:12.960 --> 00:17:14.120
JA?

00:17:13.810 --> 00:17:14.700
⟨TAMBON⟩

00:17:14.522 --> 00:17:16.400
JA, ikh ken nisht dos makhn.

00:17:16.608 --> 00:17:18.773
zogt er tsu mir, "DU

00:17:18.773 --> 00:17:20.639
du gey aroyf tsu di KRIPO

00:17:20.639 --> 00:17:22.089
loyft dort ahin

00:17:22.089 --> 00:17:23.149
un breng mir."

00:17:23.149 --> 00:17:24.549
⟨zog ikh⟩ "vemen zol ikh brengen?"

00:17:24.549 --> 00:17:26.989
dort iz do a yid vos er heyst ⟨SHASHA⟩

00:17:26.989 --> 00:17:28.029
vos der BIEBOW

00:17:28.029 --> 00:17:29.549
hot im gebrengt arayn

00:17:29.549 --> 00:17:30.269
dort.

00:17:30.269 --> 00:17:31.299
iz er geven a slikhener.

00:17:31.299 --> 00:17:34.089
er iz do do gevorn. geven a rikhtik slikhener, hot gearbet

00:17:34.089 --> 00:17:35.309
er iz geven a shofer.

00:17:35.309 --> 00:17:37.714
er hot gearbet dort. zogt er "gey breng mir

00:17:38.274 --> 00:17:39.806
dem ⟨SHASHA⟩."

00:17:39.947 --> 00:17:41.459
bin ikh gelofn arop

00:17:41.685 --> 00:17:42.961
tsu di KRIPO

00:17:43.069 --> 00:17:46.179
in geto, zogt tsu im, dem, dem, ⟨vi⟩ heyst er, dem

00:17:46.179 --> 00:17:47.377
f-

00:17:47.377 --> 00:17:51.815
⟨SUTTER⟩ az er hot mikh geshikt, FUCHS hot mikh geshikt, ikh zol brengen dem ⟨SHASHA⟩.

00:17:51.815 --> 00:17:55.567
iz er hot genumen dem ⟨SHASHA⟩ mit mir un aruntergeganen dort ahin.

00:17:55.742 --> 00:17:59.685
s'iz nisht geven vayt aribertsugeyn di brik, vayl s'iz dort di KOSCIELNA gevezn di KRIPO.

00:18:00.163 --> 00:18:02.666
m'iz aribergekumen tsu geyn. er hot geholfn.

00:18:02.666 --> 00:18:08.327
m'iz gekumen tsu geyn, farshteystu, un m'hot gekhapt vayter genumen, un m'hot getun UNK. mit eyn mol zogt er

00:18:08.327 --> 00:18:11.542
"shoyn." s'iz geven eyns a zeyger, endikt zikh

00:18:11.542 --> 00:18:12.561
di SPERRE.

00:18:12.702 --> 00:18:17.286
hot zikh geendikt di SPERRE. zey shoyn aroysgelofn, ⟨zenen⟩ mentshn ongehoybn tsu loyfn zey shoyn avek

00:18:17.376 --> 00:18:21.572
tsu UNK, tsu di ⟨kukh⟩ tsu khapn a SUPPE, tsu krign a bisl esn.

00:18:21.780 --> 00:18:25.610
s'hot nisht gedoyert keyn halbe sho. mit eyn mol kumt on tsu forn

00:18:25.610 --> 00:18:27.860
ver kumt on tsu forn fun JEEP?

00:18:27.860 --> 00:18:29.470
nokh a molt der FUCHS

00:18:29.470 --> 00:18:30.930
un der MILLER

00:18:30.930 --> 00:18:32.423
un es kumt tsu forn SCHMIDT.

00:18:32.423 --> 00:18:34.073
es kumt tsu forn der bokser.

00:18:34.683 --> 00:18:37.403
der bokser iz nisht gevezn. der bokser iz geven in Belkhetev.

00:18:37.403 --> 00:18:39.604
iz er nisht geven, hot, hobn zey gemakht UNK

00:18:39.604 --> 00:18:41.244
un hobn zey gezen

00:18:41.244 --> 00:18:42.334
⟨ongefangen⟩ tsu loyfn.

00:18:42.334 --> 00:18:44.264
zi hot dertseylt, mayn froy hot dertseylt

00:18:44.264 --> 00:18:45.709
mayn froy hot dertseylt vi nokh

00:18:45.709 --> 00:18:47.809
zey hobn gevust az UNK

00:18:47.809 --> 00:18:50.349
bay, vi nokh zey hobn gevust az

00:18:50.349 --> 00:18:52.689
bahaltn zikh, zenen zey aroysgegangen. neyn.

00:18:52.689 --> 00:18:55.789
zey hobn ongetsundn a fayer, gemakht zikh a fayer tsu makhn a bisl zup

00:18:55.789 --> 00:18:56.599
tsu makhn a bisl zup.

00:18:56.599 --> 00:18:58.823
hobn zey gezen di roykh. ikh bin dokh geven dervayl.

00:18:58.823 --> 00:18:59.953
m'hot gezen dem roykh

00:18:59.953 --> 00:19:01.333
es zenen nokh oybn do mentshn.

00:19:01.333 --> 00:19:02.873
azoy ⟨zenen mir⟩ aroyfgelofn

00:19:02.873 --> 00:19:04.259
in di tsimer arayn

00:19:04.259 --> 00:19:06.359
un azoy hobn zey aroysgekhapt di mentshn. zey hobn gezen

00:19:06.359 --> 00:19:07.629
hobn zey ge⟨UNK⟩

00:19:07.629 --> 00:19:10.215
zey hobn gekokht a bisl zup, ⟨opgemakht⟩ a bisl vaser tsi vos

00:19:10.215 --> 00:19:11.575
azoy nokh iz gevezn.

00:19:11.575 --> 00:19:14.432
un demolt, farshteystu, zenen di mentshn dortn gevezn

00:19:14.432 --> 00:19:15.852
dos KRANKENHAUS

00:19:15.852 --> 00:19:16.972
dos hot geheysn

00:19:16.972 --> 00:19:18.672
dos meshugoim KRANKENHAUS

00:19:18.672 --> 00:19:19.983
oyf yi- oyf yidish

00:19:19.983 --> 00:19:21.753
oyf poylish hot dos geheysn ⟨DOMOWIA⟩

00:19:21.753 --> 00:19:23.031
UNK

00:19:23.543 --> 00:19:25.595
UNK

00:19:25.888 --> 00:19:30.828
un di mentshn hobn ongehoybn tsu loyfn, oyf di tsveyte zayt iz geven a m- a molt a gut, dort iz geven an ALTES gut ort.

00:19:30.828 --> 00:19:32.478
zey hobn ⟨azoy⟩ ongehoybn aribertsuloyfn

00:19:32.824 --> 00:19:34.033
ibern ployt.

00:19:34.056 --> 00:19:36.596
mayne oygn, hot er aroysgenumen a mashin gever

00:19:39.640 --> 00:19:42.757
un er hot geshosn fir un tsvontsik mentshn

00:19:43.033 --> 00:19:44.664
hot er dort geshosn.

00:19:45.345 --> 00:19:47.240
der, der, der

00:19:47.240 --> 00:19:49.271
GESTAPO shef.

00:19:49.497 --> 00:19:52.463
UND farshteystu, un m'hot genumen, m'hot gekhapt

00:19:52.463 --> 00:19:56.373
un shpeter az dos ⟨hot zikh shoyn⟩ geendikt di SPERRE, hobn mir gemuzt nemen di mentshn.

00:19:56.373 --> 00:19:58.563
m'hot zey aribergetrogn arayn in di andere zayt geto

00:19:58.563 --> 00:20:00.083
aroyfgevorfn oyfn tramvay

00:20:00.083 --> 00:20:01.403
un aruntergefirt

00:20:01.663 --> 00:20:02.635
oyf dem

00:20:03.047 --> 00:20:04.104
gutn ort.

00:20:04.110 --> 00:20:07.029
dos iz geven di SPE- eyntsike SPERRE vos hot pasirt

00:20:07.029 --> 00:20:09.819
s'iz ⟨kazane⟩ SPERRE iz nisht gevezn tsvey molt

00:20:09.848 --> 00:20:11.276
eyn molt oyfn tsveytn.

00:20:11.907 --> 00:20:13.642
yo, dos iz gevezn a SPERRE.

00:20:13.642 --> 00:20:16.777
yetst vil ikh dir dertseyln ikh b- ikh bin geganen tsu shpet a bisl

00:20:16.777 --> 00:20:20.317
vos hot pasirt ven m'hot likvidirt di Varsh- di Varshever geto

00:20:21.475 --> 00:20:24.864
hot men arayngebrengt fun di Varshever geto iz arayngekumen tsu forn

00:20:24.864 --> 00:20:25.924
fil doktoyrim.

00:20:26.115 --> 00:20:27.729
s'iz gekumen tsu forn

00:20:28.782 --> 00:20:31.408
farshidene ARTZEN un s'iz gekumen tsu forn

00:20:31.482 --> 00:20:34.280
a grupe, farshteystu, vos iz gevezn

00:20:34.280 --> 00:20:36.296
di UNK in Varshe.

00:20:36.296 --> 00:20:38.094
gekumen Dovid GERTLER

00:20:38.094 --> 00:20:39.913
tsvey brider Korn

00:20:39.970 --> 00:20:43.375
un der UNK geven der grester shoy- soyne yisroel iz geven a yid.

00:20:43.375 --> 00:20:44.604
vi hot er geheysn?

00:20:45.353 --> 00:20:45.923
d-

00:20:45.923 --> 00:20:50.274
un zey hobn ongehoybn tsu makhn di zelbe gesheft mit dem FUCHS. der FUCHS iz dokh geven der hoypt

00:20:50.382 --> 00:20:52.073
tsu makhn in di geto.

00:20:52.073 --> 00:20:54.553
geganen, koydem hot men gemakht di SONDERKOMMANDO

00:20:54.553 --> 00:20:56.103
hot er gekert tsu GESTAPO.

00:20:56.119 --> 00:20:58.256
zey hobn shoyn nisht gev- UNK dort

00:20:58.819 --> 00:21:02.039
dem ko- altn komisar vos iz geven in di SONDERKOMMANDO

00:21:02.039 --> 00:21:05.597
DANZIGER hot men bazaytikt. ver iz gevorn

00:21:05.923 --> 00:21:07.453
gevorn ⟨KLUGER⟩.

00:21:07.453 --> 00:21:08.563
iz gevorn dort

00:21:08.563 --> 00:21:10.993
un Dovid GERTLER iz gevorn der hoypt man.

00:21:10.993 --> 00:21:12.920
er iz gevorn der hoypt fun di geto.

00:21:13.011 --> 00:21:14.130
er iz gevorn

00:21:14.130 --> 00:21:16.659
mer nokh fun di prezes. er iz geven mit FUCHSn.

00:21:16.659 --> 00:21:18.949
farshteyst? er hot gevust vos es hot zikh getun in Varshe.

00:21:19.761 --> 00:21:24.499
ahin un aher, farshtey- ⟨azoy⟩ hot zikh ongehoybn tsu firn a nayer posek in di geto

00:21:24.499 --> 00:21:25.815
mit a naye

00:21:25.815 --> 00:21:26.572
UNK

00:21:27.287 --> 00:21:31.757
⟨in der tsayt⟩ farshteystu, hot ⟨zikh⟩ ongehoybn tsu ma- makhn, ongehoybn tsu makhn. DAWIDOWICZ iz gevorn

00:21:31.757 --> 00:21:34.047
der komisar fun di tram- fun di

00:21:34.047 --> 00:21:36.457
ele- sh- ele- telefonen

00:21:36.923 --> 00:21:41.754
un di andere hobn ongehoybn tsu arbetn, ⟨un⟩ zey hobn ongehoybn tsu likvidirn bislekhvayz di geto, tsu makhn

00:21:41.754 --> 00:21:42.738
klener.

00:21:44.533 --> 00:21:46.299
esn iz nisht geven keyn sakh.

00:21:47.149 --> 00:21:51.869
mit eyn mol, farshteystu, iz gekumen tsu forn di komisye. s'iz gekumen tsu forn der KREISE, der hoypt

00:21:51.869 --> 00:21:53.419
fun di gantse, fun geto

00:21:53.419 --> 00:21:55.859
UNK nisht bloyz fun di geto, nor fun di

00:21:55.859 --> 00:21:57.710
shtot gekumen tsu forn

00:21:57.710 --> 00:22:02.899
un m'hot gemakht, m'hot gezen, m'hot, heybt men on tsu kvi- UNK demolt hot men nisht gevust ⟨men⟩ likvidirn

00:22:02.899 --> 00:22:06.904
hobn zey ge⟨UNK⟩, ⟨tsi⟩ hobn zey gehat vifl m'hot gefirt oyfn front aroys esn

00:22:07.315 --> 00:22:09.671
un m'hot zey bashnitn di front dort

00:22:09.778 --> 00:22:12.725
hot men gebrengt ⟨eyn⟩ molt arayn vagonen

00:22:12.850 --> 00:22:16.944
kartofl un bulkes un k-

00:22:16.944 --> 00:22:17.944
kileribn

00:22:17.944 --> 00:22:22.244
un dos hot men UNK nisht gehat vos tsu tun nisht UNK ikh hob geboyt di linye

00:22:22.244 --> 00:22:25.443
fun tramvay aroys tsu di ban, un di ayznban

00:22:25.443 --> 00:22:32.753
m'hot gemakht an UNK kuplung, az me zol kenen tsuforn mit undzere vagonen, me zol lodenen fun undz, un m'hot ongehoybn arayntsubrengen in di geto arayn dos

00:22:32.753 --> 00:22:34.339
arayntsubrengen in di geto arayn.

00:22:34.339 --> 00:22:36.739
m'hot gehat UNK. m'hot dos gemakht

00:22:36.739 --> 00:22:40.294
un dos, er hot ongehoybn, gevorn der tseleyger. er hot ⟨ge- ge- tsu teyln⟩

00:22:40.294 --> 00:22:41.565
der GERTLER

00:22:42.398 --> 00:22:46.138
iz geven a rikhtiker s- er hot gehat a shvoger, hot er geheysn Kraytshik.

00:22:46.903 --> 00:22:48.608
zayn shvoger iz geven in Varshe oykh

00:22:48.608 --> 00:22:50.018
bay di UNK.

00:22:50.018 --> 00:22:56.104
ahin un aher, s'hot zikh ongehoybn ⟨tsu⟩ mir zenen gevorn groyse ⟨mayses⟩. in di geto, fun di geto zenen aroysgeganen nokh in di k-

00:22:56.104 --> 00:22:57.536
in di shtot arayn

00:22:57.536 --> 00:22:58.408
arbetn

00:22:58.408 --> 00:23:00.447
dos hot geheysn di UNK

00:23:00.589 --> 00:23:03.619
ikh vil dir dertseyln, dos iz zeyer vikhtik tsu visn

00:23:03.619 --> 00:23:06.659
in di UNK iz gevezn punkt mayns a feter

00:23:06.659 --> 00:23:09.499
GROSKOP, hot er gehat a ⟨SMACZARNIA⟩ in di shtot

00:23:09.499 --> 00:23:11.497
un dort hobn zey tsuzamengenumen ale

00:23:11.497 --> 00:23:13.267
kleyder fun di mentshn vos m'hot tsugenumen

00:23:13.267 --> 00:23:15.397
vos ⟨m'hot⟩ avekgeshikt, hot men gebrengt dort arayn

00:23:15.397 --> 00:23:16.967
un zey hobn sortirt

00:23:16.967 --> 00:23:21.693
velekh iz gor gut, un velekh s'iz ⟨vol⟩, un velekh ⟨tsi⟩ me tserayst. dos iz geven aroysgeganen in di geto arayn

00:23:21.784 --> 00:23:23.580
zenen aroysgeganen yidn

00:23:23.580 --> 00:23:24.960
dortn mit di grupe

00:23:24.960 --> 00:23:27.941
a ⟨grup⟩ firer iz geven a Radziner. er lebt

00:23:28.028 --> 00:23:30.902
iz er geganen aroys ⟨fun⟩ di geto. vos hobn di yidn getun?

00:23:30.902 --> 00:23:33.862
zey hobn mitgenumen a shtikl gold, gold tsi a por dolar.

00:23:33.862 --> 00:23:35.532
zey hobn gegebn un gekoyft dort

00:23:35.532 --> 00:23:37.712
bay di mentshn, bay di polyakn

00:23:37.712 --> 00:23:38.922
vos ⟨iz⟩ gekumen in lager arayn

00:23:38.922 --> 00:23:42.093
hobn zey arayngebrengt UNK in di geto zol hobn tsu esn.

00:23:42.253 --> 00:23:43.322
der GERTLER

00:23:43.322 --> 00:23:45.960
hot es ge- gevorn tsu vis- ge- tsu visn

00:23:46.708 --> 00:23:49.954
in di fri morgn, ikh n- for ikh halb zibn

00:23:49.954 --> 00:23:52.864
muz ikh aroysforn in BALUTER plats aroysforn mitn vogn

00:23:52.864 --> 00:23:56.954
ikh kum arop tsu tsu d- UNK git er a kum tsu mir der Dovid GERTLER

00:23:56.954 --> 00:23:58.544
"du muzst zayn do far mir."

00:23:58.544 --> 00:24:00.373
zog ikh "vos taytsh ikh vel zayn bay dir?

00:24:00.373 --> 00:24:02.813
ikh ken nisht shteyn. ikh muz geyn aroys mitn tramvay."

00:24:02.813 --> 00:24:06.227
"neyn, du vest nisht forn mitn tramvay. du muzst UNK zayn do mit mir."

00:24:06.992 --> 00:24:10.276
un es kumen tsvey dray politsyantn kumen

00:24:10.350 --> 00:24:11.452
mit

00:24:11.452 --> 00:24:14.276
vos iz? "di mentshn zoln aroysgeyn."

00:24:15.615 --> 00:24:17.263
gekumen in a grupe tsu geyn

00:24:17.725 --> 00:24:20.755
hot men zey araynge- arayngekhapt in di, in barakn arayn

00:24:20.755 --> 00:24:22.135
"⟨muzst⟩ bazukhn" zogt er.

00:24:22.135 --> 00:24:27.315
"gets op dos, gets op dos harte, gets op di veykhe, git op dos, un ver s'vet nisht opgebn

00:24:27.315 --> 00:24:28.904
vet shoyn mer nisht

00:24:28.904 --> 00:24:29.869
aroysgeyn."

00:24:31.545 --> 00:24:35.769
a sakh hobn gegebn, un a sakh hobn nisht gegebn. UNK arayngenumen tsu geyn dort in di barakn.

00:24:35.769 --> 00:24:38.259
ikh bin geshtanen in droysn mitn vogn UNK

00:24:38.430 --> 00:24:42.165
iz geshtanen der politsyant, der NIMAN iz geven a pol- yidisher politsyant

00:24:42.165 --> 00:24:43.667
fun ershtn revir

00:24:43.667 --> 00:24:46.977
⟨iz⟩ er geshtanen oykhet, un UNK m'hot bazukht di mentshn.

00:24:46.977 --> 00:24:48.627
m'hot nebekh aroysgenumen

00:24:48.977 --> 00:24:51.266
⟨undzer⟩ harte. m'hot aroysgenumen di veykhe

00:24:51.627 --> 00:24:55.924
iz do a grupe UNK. mit eyn molt iz gekumen tsu forn der yeke

00:24:55.930 --> 00:24:57.561
fun di shtot

00:24:57.617 --> 00:24:59.349
nemen di mentshn

00:25:00.385 --> 00:25:01.982
mit zeyere STRASSENBAHN.

00:25:03.642 --> 00:25:07.002
iz er tsugan nemen, zogt er UNK, zogt er "kumts aroys."

00:25:07.500 --> 00:25:11.516
zogt er "neyn." hot er gegebn a khap aroys der revolver, der fun di shtot.

00:25:12.315 --> 00:25:13.660
"ikh knal dikh avek."

00:25:14.256 --> 00:25:17.290
hot zikh geefnt di tir, azoy vi do shteyt do dort

00:25:17.290 --> 00:25:20.024
un s'iz aroysgan der komisar FUCHS, zogt er "DA

00:25:20.024 --> 00:25:21.472
HIER BIST DU MICH

00:25:21.664 --> 00:25:23.424
do bistu mikh, nisht du.

00:25:23.424 --> 00:25:24.610
rir mikh nisht."

00:25:26.457 --> 00:25:30.947
farshteyst? er hot gehat a hekhere range, hot men nisht getun gornisht. m'hot di mentshn bazukht.

00:25:30.947 --> 00:25:33.207
helftn zenen shoyn nisht avekgeganen

00:25:33.207 --> 00:25:34.657
un helft hot men avekgeshikt.

00:25:34.928 --> 00:25:36.626
tsvey tog shpeter

00:25:37.560 --> 00:25:41.025
ale mentshn oyf di UNK avek- avekgeshikt.

00:25:41.025 --> 00:25:44.145
farshteyst? azoy, dos iz gevezn der Dovid GERTLER.

00:25:44.145 --> 00:25:45.965
⟨dos⟩ bist nisht fertik mit dem.

00:25:45.965 --> 00:25:48.320
nokh dem hot zikh ongehoybn vayter WYSIEDLENIAs.

00:25:48.833 --> 00:25:51.113
WYSIEDLENIAs hot men ongehoybn UNK undz genumen

00:25:51.113 --> 00:25:53.473
oyf MARYSIN, hobn zey ge- likvidirt MARYSIN

00:25:54.503 --> 00:25:55.803
di kinder.

00:25:55.803 --> 00:25:57.703
dort iz geven kinder ⟨zey⟩ gehat, un m'hot ge-

00:25:57.703 --> 00:26:01.035
m- zi iz oykh gevezn, mayn eygene froy, dort geven a g- lererin.

00:26:01.035 --> 00:26:02.895
m'hot dort avekgefirt di kinder

00:26:02.895 --> 00:26:07.169
un dernokh dem hot men genumen, farshtey- eltere mentshn, m'hot gekhapt di kinder, m'hot a- sh- avekgeshikt

00:26:07.868 --> 00:26:10.950
UNK az dos iz g- ⟨eyns⟩. yetst, farshteystu

00:26:11.125 --> 00:26:12.519
dokter Miler

00:26:12.677 --> 00:26:14.741
er iz geven der ⟨OBERLEKTOR⟩ fun shpitol

00:26:14.741 --> 00:26:17.281
s'iz geven a bisl, froy hot zikh dos badarft tsu dertseyln

00:26:17.281 --> 00:26:18.751
nor ikh dertseyl es yetst.

00:26:19.393 --> 00:26:22.711
dokter Miler hot gehat a tokhter. dokter Miler iz geven a yeke.

00:26:23.916 --> 00:26:28.146
UND a d- zeyer a sheyne tokhter hot er gehat UNK, un er iz bakant mit BIEBOWn.

00:26:28.146 --> 00:26:29.666
hot BIEBOW gezogt

00:26:29.666 --> 00:26:32.178
ikh vel dir di tokhter aroysnemen, oyser di geto.

00:26:33.079 --> 00:26:35.519
in fri morgn, m'iz gekumen do mitn tramvay

00:26:35.519 --> 00:26:36.589
aroysgeforn

00:26:36.589 --> 00:26:40.589
mit di tokhter ahingeforn. BIEBOW hot gehat dort oyser di geto far, lebn di geto bald

00:26:40.589 --> 00:26:42.459
⟨RADA⟩ gas heyst dos do

00:26:42.459 --> 00:26:44.772
hot er gehat a hoyz, un m'hot getrunken UNK

00:26:44.772 --> 00:26:46.286
getrunken, ahin aher.

00:26:46.512 --> 00:26:49.088
er hot dort farshteystu genumen di tokhter ahin

00:26:49.313 --> 00:26:51.517
un, iz er ⟨aropganen⟩. UNK veys ⟨ikh⟩.

00:26:52.924 --> 00:26:54.268
a vokh shpeter

00:26:55.033 --> 00:26:56.543
zogt tsu mir miler

00:26:56.543 --> 00:27:02.023
v- "ikh hob" zogt er "nisht gekrign" zogt er "fun mayn tokhter keyn entfer." er hot gevolt visn. zog ikh "ikh ken dir gornisht tun."

00:27:04.450 --> 00:27:07.262
geforn aroys. bin aroysgeforn dort ahin

00:27:07.352 --> 00:27:08.561
oyfn gutn ort

00:27:08.719 --> 00:27:10.682
me muz adurkhforn durkh dem gutn ort

00:27:10.682 --> 00:27:12.392
zogt mir der bagreber

00:27:12.583 --> 00:27:13.724
"vos zukhstu?

00:27:14.727 --> 00:27:16.307
UNK arayngeyn tsun im?

00:27:16.785 --> 00:27:20.415
er hot bagrobn di tokhter un m'hot UNK bagrobn di tokhter un aribergeforn mitn

00:27:20.415 --> 00:27:21.875
mit dem JEEP.

00:27:21.875 --> 00:27:23.310
zi ligt shoyn dort in der erd.

00:27:24.396 --> 00:27:25.925
dos iz geven dokter Miler's.

00:27:26.134 --> 00:27:27.832
yetst iz do SPERRES.

00:27:28.108 --> 00:27:31.548
ongehoybn f- naye SPERRES. un mir hobn ge- ikh hob gehat mayn ⟨kontur⟩

00:27:31.548 --> 00:27:32.535
oyf di

00:27:32.535 --> 00:27:33.907
FRANCISZKANSKA

00:27:34.352 --> 00:27:36.894
akhtn s- akht un akhtsik

00:27:37.187 --> 00:27:41.587
un UNK hot zikh gedreyt aroys dort tsum gutn ort.

00:27:41.587 --> 00:27:42.777
dort iz geven eyner

00:27:42.777 --> 00:27:45.067
der komisar hot geheysn ⟨BERNSTEIN⟩

00:27:45.692 --> 00:27:46.732
a yeke.

00:27:47.413 --> 00:27:50.073
er hot gefirt dem, dort hot men gemakht di kholevkes.

00:27:52.054 --> 00:27:57.347
vegn vos dertseyl ikh dos? d- dort iz geven a yid, farshteystu, un m'hot ge- er hot genumen a shtikele leder

00:27:57.707 --> 00:27:59.287
un zey hobn im gekhapt.

00:27:59.513 --> 00:28:01.059
ibergebn di daytshn.

00:28:01.420 --> 00:28:02.665
hot men im gebrengt

00:28:02.665 --> 00:28:03.911
un m'hot im gehongen.

00:28:04.778 --> 00:28:08.038
azoy UNK ⟨shir⟩ gevorn, nokh dem az s'iz gevorn

00:28:08.038 --> 00:28:10.708
m'hot dem ershtn mentsh dort gehongen, iz gevorn

00:28:10.708 --> 00:28:13.479
a UNK. s'iz geven a yidisher sond.

00:28:13.873 --> 00:28:18.303
hot men gevolt, der prezes hot gevolt di daytshn ⟨zoln⟩ gebn ⟨a bafel⟩ er zol

00:28:18.303 --> 00:28:20.443
der sond zol

00:28:20.443 --> 00:28:22.253
gebn toyt shtrof.

00:28:22.253 --> 00:28:23.863
⟨oyf⟩ dort iz gevezn

00:28:23.863 --> 00:28:27.506
UNK mayns a mishpokhe. er iz do, iz do geshtorbn in YISRAEL.

00:28:27.506 --> 00:28:30.166
⟨BRONOSKI⟩, der SEDZIA ⟨BRONOSKI⟩

00:28:30.166 --> 00:28:33.164
un der SEDZIA, ikh hob di bilder mit zey, un der SEDZIA ⟨FAJN⟩

00:28:33.164 --> 00:28:36.454
un der SEDZIA, nokh eyner hot er geheysn, hot men nisht gevolt gebn.

00:28:38.325 --> 00:28:40.833
⟨BRONOSKIN⟩ hot men avekgeshikt. er iz geven oyf Poyzn.

00:28:41.143 --> 00:28:42.667
un di andere avek

00:28:42.667 --> 00:28:44.077
un der sond iz gevezn.

00:28:44.077 --> 00:28:47.217
nokh dem hot men gemakht di andere mentshn araynkumen ⟨oyf⟩ a sond arayn

00:28:47.217 --> 00:28:51.177
hot men ge- eyner hot geganvet, iz geven akh- dos iz UNK untervelt mentshn, ongefaln

00:28:51.177 --> 00:28:52.617
Yankl CHMOL

00:28:52.838 --> 00:28:54.151
mit z- mayn khevre

00:28:54.151 --> 00:28:55.870
hobn geganvet aroys mel

00:28:56.112 --> 00:28:57.532
hot men zey gebroykht

00:28:57.532 --> 00:28:59.862
hot men undz gemakht di tlies, zey hengen

00:29:00.145 --> 00:29:01.674
hot men zey geshenkt

00:29:01.967 --> 00:29:05.684
dem, dem UNK un m'hot genumen an andern mentsh

00:29:05.684 --> 00:29:07.184
un m'hot gehongen.

00:29:07.184 --> 00:29:10.059
hot men gehongen demolt finef perzonen

00:29:10.059 --> 00:29:12.659
un mir ale hobn gemuzt geyn fun di geto UNK

00:29:12.659 --> 00:29:14.289
vos hobn gevoynt ⟨in⟩ di andere zayt

00:29:14.289 --> 00:29:15.347
dort oyf dem

00:29:15.347 --> 00:29:17.807
d- aribertsugeyn zen vi me hengt zey.
